**Test procedure:** Analyze the TLS configuration of the OpenMRS domain using an SSL/TLS analysis tool; verify HTTPS enforcement; verify MySQL connection requires TLS.

**Test execution:**

TLS analysis of [openmrs-domain]: Protocol support — TLS 1.2, TLS 1.3 supported; TLS 1.0, 1.1 not supported. ✓ Cipher suites — ECDHE key exchange present; no weak ciphers (RC4, DES, 3DES) listed. ✓ Certificate — valid, not expired, issued by ACM, domain matches. ✓ HSTS header — present. ✓

